comments: I noticed that the word were pretty similiar and easy to learn, I also noticed that "Zeticoh" was the only word different from the others, having "coh" at the end, since the other colors of the same shape were all "zeticom". I only used memory. The difficult part was the one with the partner, I suspect that we learned the same words for the shapes, but a different variation for some colors, since we had some difficulty in chosing the right shape as the role of receiver.
